# Supabase (future)

**Status:** Dormant — marketing v2 is static today. Activate when adding Supabase-backed config or analytics storage.

## When adding Supabase

- Follow patterns from `onetap-app` / `onetap-marketing` v1:
  - RLS on all user-owned tables.
  - Service role only on server; anon key client-safe only for intended reads.
  - Migrations in `supabase/migrations/` with explicit policies.

## Safe changes

- Mirror `onetap-app/.cursor/skills/supabase-safe-change/SKILL.md` for migration + RLS checklists.
- Never expose `SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY` to the client.

## Env

- Document new vars in `.env.example`, `docs/engineering/environment-variables.md`, and `.github/workflows/quality-gates.yml`.
